00:09.810 --> 00:12.311
Cough, cough. Sniffle.

00:13.514 --> 00:15.214
No, no, no, no.
You can't be sick.

00:15.216 --> 00:16.915
I don't know how to do
this life thing alone.

00:16.917 --> 00:19.418
I think i have
the foo foo plague.

00:21.188 --> 00:23.188
You do? And what do
you take for that?

00:23.190 --> 00:24.523
Foo foo medicine.

00:24.525 --> 00:28.193
