00:38.906 --> 00:40.739
Yep. Crushing weight.
Yep, yep.

00:40.741 --> 00:42.808
(yelps)

00:42.810 --> 00:45.778
Oh, no! Oh, no!
Maya, i really do.

00:45.780 --> 00:48.914
I have the foo foos!
It's like there's an elephant
on my chest.

00:50.351 --> 00:52.384
I am at most
a labradoodle.

00:53.954 --> 00:56.388
Maya, you have to get
far, far away from me.

00:56.390 --> 00:57.656
I don't want you
to catch this.

00:57.658 --> 00:59.658
I know.
That would be terrible.

01:01.228 --> 01:02.361
(sighs)

01:03.664 --> 01:07.399
(giggles)

01:08.269 --> 01:10.903
Okay, now can we please
go to school now
and get out of rileytown?

01:13.607 --> 01:15.741
What? I just said,
"can we get out
of rileytow--" oof.

01:17.411 --> 01:19.411
What is it with you?
That's just a word i made up.

01:19.413 --> 01:20.879
I know what it means.

01:20.881 --> 01:23.282
It means that i'm goofy
and silly and weird.

01:23.284 --> 01:25.617
-It means you're unique.
-I don't want to be unique.

01:26.587 --> 01:28.353
I don't want
anybody to notice me.

01:28.355 --> 01:30.589
Since when?
Rileytown is where you live.

01:30.591 --> 01:33.358
We even made your own flag
and national anthem, remember?

01:34.361 --> 01:37.396
♪ rileytown, oh rileytown ♪

01:37.398 --> 01:38.564
Whee.

01:39.900 --> 01:41.400
Yeah, that took us
four days to write.

01:43.571 --> 01:46.038
Is this serious
or are we having fun?

01:46.040 --> 01:47.606
You are a bully.

01:47.608 --> 01:49.942
Okay, that's not fun.

01:49.944 --> 01:51.510
I don't like
being laughed at, maya.

01:51.512 --> 01:52.744
Nobody likes being laughed at.

01:52.746 --> 01:55.347
I'm not laughing at you.
Who's laughing at you?

01:57.418 --> 01:59.451
You never should have
come up with it,
and you're a bully.

01:59.453 --> 02:00.686
Okay?

